ckquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/1s9zajwt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1s9zajwt&h=947f3319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想食咩就自己煮咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好正喎 但唔食菜 無便便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n菜叮完太頹無影，其實一定會有一格菜一格主食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多菜叮完都唔好食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好唔好食一回事，靚唔靚仔又一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想好食唔頹就整瓜最好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西蘭花同瓜帶飯都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n葉菜叮完好似唔健康，會釋放唔知乜鳩<br />\n瓜莖類最好<br />\n<br />\n不過通常都係另外整茶記碟頭飯為主<br />\n可以用電飯煲整蒸飯，仲正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a063206a48903496938e886a8906ce9e9ecd95b","tid":27202,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帶到好悶 來來去去都係幾味 有咩菜式推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦 <br />\n<br />\n帶飯不嬲係睇前一晚食咩咪帶咩<br />\n<br />\n會特登為左帶飯而去煮架咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶琴晚既餸x2</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老母嗰啲太難食，會另外整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828f60471951fd4d57ba6ab32929088ab819f928","tid":27202,"uid":51326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:19:09.000Z","msg":"食返前一晚啲餸炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n帶飯為慳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e922fa2246a6ea9aacef102025e701c5166adc","tid":27202,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:56:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/1s9zajwt\" data-thumbnail-sr