碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"e3e4749b19a397cecbae673ce6db4c9c72cd88d4","tid":27202,"uid":15144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>炒烏冬 炒飯 叮極都咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煮呢啲就菜同肉就可以落埋落去 方便啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1vnMu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1vnMu7.jpg&h=13fd3e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1N02W21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1N02W21.jpg&h=524b6e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金菇肥牛都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n西蘭花 點解會變到咁碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n切碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶得炒多個餸"},{"pid":"5383b42ebec614023acfce4dacdeda98de8fb0f7","tid":27202,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:58:41.000Z","msg":"炒下烏冬 有時整下雞翼 炒下飯咁"},{"pid":"44150d6b73c7b7af9088e7bdd436e3c89fc1c81c","tid":27202,"uid":40744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:04:30.000Z","msg":"飯加煎午餐肉/腸仔<br />\n午餐肉炒飯 有五香肉丁會加埋<br />\n有時懶得整就營多撈麵<br />\n豐富啲嘅試過煎宜家啲三文魚柳加小小鹽<br />\n又或者肉丸加辣椒油<br />\n<br />\n應該好快死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513bfe547ce01d98e81157890a5a9db43a9c3088","tid":27202,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T03:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飯加煎午餐肉/腸仔<br />\n午餐肉炒飯 有五香肉丁會加埋<br />\n有時懶得整就營多撈麵<br />\n豐富啲嘅試過煎宜家啲三文魚柳加小小鹽<br />\n又或者肉丸加辣椒油<br />\n<br />\n應該好快死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今日煮左個麵 一陣落湯落去叮 好撚頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889e2a15557ddbfe6201281e249